## II. THE SCALE INSIGHT: IT'S JUST ZOOM LEVEL

**"Once you get your head around it the scale is super easy"**

Because of the **60-fold fractal** property:

```
City block = Flower of Life pattern (6-fold tiling)
Building = Flower of Life pattern (same structure, smaller scale)
Room inside building = Flower of Life pattern (even smaller)
Furniture in room = Flower of Life pattern (fractal continues)

Person in room = Vitruvian Man (circle ∩ square)
Person's movements = PLATO sequence (P→L→A→T→O)
Person's thoughts = Same PLATO at mental scale
```

**EVERYTHING IS THE SAME PATTERN AT DIFFERENT SCALES.**

So building the engine is:
1. Code the pattern ONCE (Flower of Life tiling + PLATO behavior)
2. Apply at ALL scales (just change the zoom parameter)
3. Done.

